profile: For over 40 years, we have helped Ontario homeowners and builders build safer, more energy-efficient and sustainable communities. With a broad range of products and services, we are your insulation experts for existing home renovation upgrades and new residential home construction—satisfaction guaranteed. Proudly serving all of Southern Ontario, we are Ontario's largest insulation company and are Energy Star and Foam Masters™ certified. Get in touch for a Free In-Home Assessment—contact us today to learn more.
products:
✓ Spray Foam (1/2 lb open cell)
✓ HFO Spray Foam (2 lb closed cell), 
✓ Cellulose (Blown and dense-pack)
✓ Fibreglass (Batts, blown and blanket wrap)
✓ Mineral Wool (Batts)
✓ Hemp (Batts)
services:
We install insulation throughout the home:
✓ Attic Insulation 
✓ Walls Insulation 
✓ Basement Insulation 
✓ Crawlspace Insulation 
✓ Garage Insulation 
✓ Floors Insulation
brands: We offer high performance, brand name insulation backed by third party warranties. Our certified installers are professionally trained to install all types of insulation.

profile:
General Contractor:

Boase Design will take an existing space and make it into the home you’ll love to live in.

We begin with a consultation, the purpose of the consultation is to listen. Listen to your wants, needs, desires, and what you envision your ideal home to be like.

Fine workmanship and exclusive use of skilled trades make for a project that runs smoothly and ends with client satisfaction. Boase Design is adamant about making sure you are well taken care of.

Boase Design takes pride in doing things right, on time, and on budget.

WE ARE ALWAYS THERE FOR OUR CLIENTS. WE DO WHAT WE SAY WE WILL DO WHEN WE SAID WE WOULD DO IT. IN SHORT WE STICK TO OUR WORD.

There are too many stories of contractors who disappear for days or weeks with no rhyme or reason, this will not happen at Boase Design, we are vigilant about open communication with our clients and are on site daily with our projects: rain or shine, sleet or snow, we get the job done.

Specific Projects:
Kitchen Renovation
Bathroom Renovation
Basement Renovation
Room and Floor plan designs
Decks
New Structures
Fences
Living room design
Structural changes and layouts
Exterior doors
Windows

brands: we use name brand products for our clients projects. We find the name brand products stand up better over time and tend to have better warranties
specialities: Boase Design is a whole home specialist.  From the front door to the back door, Boase Design has the experience to get your job done right, on time and on budget.
project_rate: Project cost is provided upon completion of estimate.
warranty_terms: 1 year warranty on all work and manufacturers warranty
